-- Amazon to Offer Video on Demand in France Next Year, Echos Says
-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 2012-10-09T16:14:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-09/amazon-to-offer-video-on-demand-in-france-next-year-echos-says.html
Amazon.com Inc. (AMZN)  plans to offer a
video on demand service in  France  from March 2013, financial
daily Les Echos reported, citing an unidentified executive from
French pay-tv company  Canal Plus .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
